FT  28 MAY 94 / London Stock Exchange: Equity futures and options trading
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Stock index futures came under heavy pressure, responding to selling by US
investment banks.
After opening at 3,015 and moving ahead to 3,024 in quiet trading, the June
