UK official reserves (May). US leading indicators (April). Mr Jacques
Delors, president of the Euro pean Commission, visits Romania (until June
4). European Union health ministers meet in Luxembourg. British Chambers of
Commerce annual conference in Birmingham (until Friday). Institute for
