364,000 exceptional gain on the sale of Sussex County Press - from turnover
of Pounds 13.9m previously.
Operating profit, including a first year contribution of Pounds 144,000 from
acquisitions, was Pounds 1.75m (Pounds 1.21m).
Earnings per share came out at 7.63p (6.59p) and a final dividend of 2p
makes a 2.95p (2.1p) total.
