amounting to Pounds 298,000, were an important factor.
Turnover improved from Pounds 17.9m to Pounds 19.1m, with the final three
months generating only 1.5 per cent of growth.
Losses per share emerged at 6.6p (earnings 9.81p). However, the final
dividend is maintained at 4.25p, making an 8.1p (7.85p) total.
Capital expenditure of Pounds 1.16m pushed year-end gearing up from 15 per
cent to 38 per cent.
